## Time-Delayed Triple Licensing

This project uses a time-delayed licensing strategy to balance protection against parasitic forks with eventual open access.

### For Recent Versions (Released within the last 16 months)

You may choose between:

**Option A: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0)**
- Free to use, modify, and distribute
- Must share modifications under AGPL-3.0
- Network use triggers source disclosure
- See full AGPL-3.0 terms below

**Option B: Commercial License**
- Use in proprietary/closed-source products
- No obligation to share modifications
- Priority support included
- Contact: https://github.com/Theadd/kiro-agents#commercial-license

### For Legacy Versions (Released more than 16 months ago)

**MIT License**
- Free to use, modify, and distribute
- Use in proprietary products without restrictions
- Minimal requirements (attribution only)
- See full MIT terms below

