## GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3.0

Full AGPL-3.0 license text:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt


### AGPL-3.0 Summary (Not Legal Advice)

The AGPL-3.0 requires that:
- You must share your source code if you distribute the software
- You must share your source code if you run it as a network service (SaaS, web app, etc.)
- Modifications must also be licensed under AGPL-3.0
- You must preserve copyright and license notices
- You must provide installation instructions

For full legal terms, see: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.txt

